=== lspci === <!--T:24-->

<!--T:25-->
{{c|lspci}} should display <code>iwlwifi</code> for both <code>Kernel driver in use:</code> and <code>Kernel modules:</code>.

<!--T:26-->
{{RootCmd|lspci -k|output=<pre>xx:xx.x Network controller: Intel Corporation Wireless xxxx
        Kernel driver in use: iwlwifi
        Kernel modules: iwlwifi
</pre>}}

<!--T:27-->
The <code>xx:xx.x</code> identifier will be useful for grepping specific information from dmesg.

=== dmesg === <!--T:28-->

<!--T:29-->
Check the output of dmesg. Replace <code>xx:xx.x</code> with the identifier from [[#lspci|lspci]] and <code>wlan</code> with the [[#Network_device_names|network interface name]].

<!--T:30-->
{{Cmd|dmesg {{!}} grep -i -E 'xx:xx.x{{!}}wlan{{!}}iwl{{!}}80211'}}

